interpretation: The "wastebasket" card represents letting go of what no longer serves you. It is a reminder to release negative thoughts, emotions, and relationships that are holding you back. This card urges you to declutter your life and make space for new opportunities and growth. It can also signify the need to be more mindful of your environmental impact and reduce waste in your daily life. Remember that sometimes it is necessary to discard things in order to create space for something better.
